@startuml
title Completed state diagram of the alarm clock

[*] --> Unprepared

state Unprepared
state Prepared
state Ringing

Ringing : do / ring

Unprepared --> Prepared : prepared(alarmTime)
Prepared --> Unprepared : unprepared
Prepared --> Ringing : [currentTime == alarmTime]
Ringing --> Prepared : stopRinging

@enduml